<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 06:22:03 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>股市为特朗普的胜利欢呼，但关税给 2025 年带来了未知数</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/stocks-cheered-trumps-victory-tariffs-bring-unknowns-2025-2024-12-11/</link><description>美国股市欢迎唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 在 2024 年总统大选中获胜，但如果当选总统兑现关税威胁，未来可能会出现动荡。</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 06:06:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/stocks-cheered-trumps-victory-tariffs-bring-unknowns-2025-2024-12-11/</guid></item><item><title>TikTok 加拿大子公司寻求对关闭令进行司法审查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/tiktoks-canada-unit-seeks-judicial-review-shutdown-orders-2024-12-11/</link><description>TikTok 加拿大部门周二在一份声明中表示，该公司已向加拿大联邦法院提出紧急动议，寻求对该公司出于国家安全考虑而关闭其在该国业务的命令进行司法审查。</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 05:23:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/tiktoks-canada-unit-seeks-judicial-review-shutdown-orders-2024-12-11/</guid></item><item><title>印度档案：中美贸易交火</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-file-us-china-trade-crossfire-2024-12-11/</link><description>本文最初发表在每周二出版的《印度档案》时事通讯上。在此注册，了解印度的最新消息以及它对世界的重要性。</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 04:35:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-file-us-china-trade-crossfire-2024-12-11/</guid></item><item><title>特斯拉12月第一周在华销量达21,900辆，创第四季度最高</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-sells-21900-evs-china-first-week-dec-highest-q4-2024-12-11/</link><description>特斯拉中国周三表示，12月第一周，美国汽车制造商特斯拉在中国销售了21,900辆电动汽车，创2024年第四季度最高单周销量。</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 03:31:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-sells-21900-evs-china-first-week-dec-highest-q4-2024-12-11/</guid></item><item><title>美国导弹防御系统能否保护关岛免受中国威胁？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/can-us-missile-defense-system-shield-guam-chinese-threat-2024-12-11/</link><description>周二晚间，一枚 SM-3 拦截弹冲上关岛上空，加速飞向目标：一枚弹道导弹，其发动机短暂照亮了关岛的东北角。</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 02:40:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/can-us-missile-defense-system-shield-guam-chinese-threat-2024-12-11/</guid></item><item><title>股市紧张等待美国消费物价指数</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-12-11/</link><description>亚洲股市和美元周三稍作喘息，此前加拿大预计将降息，而美国通胀数据预计将使美联储再次降息。</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 02:29:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-12-11/</guid></item><item><title>中国表示将采取“必要措施”捍卫台湾主权</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-reports-continued-surge-chinese-military-activity-2024-12-11/</link><description>中国政府周三表示，将采取“必要措施”捍卫国家主权，不会容忍“分裂主义”活动，因为台湾报道中国战机再次在台湾附近崛起。</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 01:51:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-reports-continued-surge-chinese-military-activity-2024-12-11/</guid></item><item><title>中国“宽松”货币政策带来的需求希望推动油价上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/oil-prices-edge-up-demand-hopes-chinas-looser-monetary-policy-2024-12-11/</link><description>周三油价上涨，市场参与者预计，在北京宣布实行宽松的货币政策以刺激中国经济增长后，全球最大原油进口国的需求将会增加。</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 01:41:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/oil-prices-edge-up-demand-hopes-chinas-looser-monetary-policy-2024-12-11/</guid></item><item><title>美国官员称，中国海军的部署与其他大型演习一致</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/chinese-naval-deployments-line-with-other-large-drills-us-official-says-2024-12-11/</link><description>一位不愿透露姓名的美国军方官员周二表示，中国在东海和南海的海军部署有所增加，但与过去的其他大型演习一致。</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 00:28:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/chinese-naval-deployments-line-with-other-large-drills-us-official-says-2024-12-11/</guid></item><item><title>亚行下调亚洲发展中国家增长预测，并提示美国政策风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/adb-trims-developing-asias-growth-forecast-flags-us-policy-risks-2024-12-11/</link><description>亚洲开发银行周三表示，今年和明年亚洲发展中国家的增长速度可能比此前预期的要慢，如果当选总统唐纳德·特朗普迅速改变美国贸易政策，前景可能会恶化。</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 00:03:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/adb-trims-developing-asias-growth-forecast-flags-us-policy-risks-2024-12-11/</guid></item><item><title>据日经新闻报道，日产在管理层改组中将首席财务官马云重新任命为中国区负责人</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/boards-policy-regulation/nissan-cfo-ma-head-china-management-reshuffle-nikkei-says-2024-12-10/</link><description>据《日经新闻》报道，日产汽车董事会已决定重新任命首席财务官马云来领导其中国业务，这对这家遭受危机打击的日本汽车制造商来说是一次高调的重组，因为该公司裁员数千人。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 23:43:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/boards-policy-regulation/nissan-cfo-ma-head-china-management-reshuffle-nikkei-says-2024-12-10/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：把筹码从桌面上拿下来，寻求中国的澄清</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-12-10/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 21:55:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-12-10/</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯机构报道俄罗斯安全官员梅德韦杰夫抵达中国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/russian-security-official-medvedev-arrives-china-russian-agencies-report-2024-12-10/</link><description>据俄罗斯新闻机构周二晚间报道，俄罗斯高级安全官员德米特里·梅德韦杰夫抵达北京，与中国领导人进行为期两天的会谈。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 21:20:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/russian-security-official-medvedev-arrives-china-russian-agencies-report-2024-12-10/</guid></item><item><title>墨西哥下议院一致批准针对应用程序工人的劳工改革</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/mexicos-lower-house-approves-labor-reform-app-workers-2024-12-10/</link><description>墨西哥下议院周二批准了一项改革，旨在通过确保获得社会保障和圣诞奖金等福利来规范滴滴、Rappi 和 Uber 等应用程序的送货员和司机的劳动条件。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 21:04:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/mexicos-lower-house-approves-labor-reform-app-workers-2024-12-10/</guid></item><item><title>瑞穗董事小林表示企业不应对特朗普的关税威胁反应过度</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/mizuho-director-kobayashi-says-companies-should-not-overreact-trumps-tariff-2024-12-10/</link><description>日本瑞穗金融、欧姆龙和全日空的董事小林泉周二表示，企业不应对当选总统唐纳德·特朗普对中国商品征收关税的威胁反应过度。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 19:10:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/mizuho-director-kobayashi-says-companies-should-not-overreact-trumps-tariff-2024-12-10/</guid></item></channel></rss>